Injector/Double Punch/Bumblebee:



Bumblebee fired off a single optic blast at Terrorsaur, heading back for the 
Predacon base, deciding he didn't want to go TO far out.

---

Double Punch watched Injector hit the ground, and TK crash 15 ft away.  
"Riiiiight..." he siad, raising a pincher, firing off an energy-signature 
seeking missile at TK's torso.

Injector got up, picking up his stinger missile launcher, smiling evilly, 
launching into the air.
